form.signup(name='loginForm' ng-submit='$ctrl.login(loginForm.$valid)' role='form' novalidate)
  label.login-text 
    | Email
  input.login-input(type='email' id='email' name='email' ng-model='$ctrl.user.email' ng-class='{ "frm-error-input" : $ctrl.loginAuthError }' required)
  .frm-error-text(ng-show='loginForm.email.$invalid && !loginForm.email.$pristine')
    | Email invalido
  label.login-text 
    | Contraseña
  input.login-input(type='password' id='password' name='password' ng-class='{ "frm-error-input" : $ctrl.loginAuthError }' ng-model='$ctrl.user.password' ng-minlength='8' ng-maxlength='52' pattern='(?=.*\d)(?=.*[a-z]).*$' required)
  .frm-error-text(ng-show='$ctrl.loginAuthError')
    | Email o contraseña incorrecto
  button.btn-login(type='submit' ng-disabled='loginForm.$invalid') 
    | Iniciar Sesion
  a.finalMessage(ui-sref='registration')
    | ¿No tienes cuenta? Click aquí
